# agentatlas-services — project context

NestJS API for **agentatlas**. Paired with **`agentatlas-platform`**.

| Repo | Role |
|------|------|
| **`agentatlas-services`** (this repo) | Backend — auth, users, swarms, inference, tools, scraper |
| **`agentatlas-platform`** | Next.js — swarm editor, test panel, admin |

When changing HTTP contracts, update this repo first; align `agentatlas-platform/src/data/api/server/`.

## Product scope

Swarms platform: auth, users, swarms orchestrator, inference, tools, and scraper.

## Core modules

- `src/swarms/` — orchestrator, graphs, runs, workers
- `src/inference/` — LLM providers
- `src/tools/` — agent function registry
- `src/auth/`, `src/users/` — auth & accounts

## Platform client

- API client: `agentatlas-platform/src/data/api/server/index.ts`
- Swarm workspace UI spec: `docs/SWARMS-WORKSPACE.md`
- Streaming: `docs/INFERENCE.md`
